---
import github from "@img/github.svg"

import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '@components/Header.astro';
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Projects">
  <body>
    <div class="my-container">
      <Header />
      <main>
        <div class="flex-grid">
          <div class="container post">
            <div class="inner">
              <div class="page-title">
                <h1>Projects 🧰</h1>
              </div>
              <div class="centered-div">
                <p>This is a list of my ongoing personal projects. They are open source and if you find yourself here and would like to contribute please do!</p>
              </div>
              <div class="centered-div">
                <h2>A couple of sites I'm working on:</h2>
                <p class="post-text">
                  <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://shoveltoss.com">shoveltoss.com</a> is the official website for the best event of all time.
                  Spun it up with <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://gohugo.io">Hugo</a>; we'll see how that goes. (Edit: Working on Vue / Tailwind rewrite lol)</p>
                <p class="post-text">
                  <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://playn-olde-recipy.herokuapp.com">playn olde recipy</a> is my fork of <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://plainoldrecipe.com">plain old recipe</a>
                  which I decided to also host until the maintainer decides to accept my pr's :)</p>
              </div>
              <div class="centered-div p-2">
                <div class="flex flex-row">
                  <h2 class="mr-2">btfd</h2>
                  <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://github.com/MaxRickettsUy/btfd">
                    <img width="20" height="20" src={github}/>
                  </a>
                </div>
                <p class="post-text"><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.mongodb.com/mern-stack">MERN</a> application for tracking holdings (currently stocks, crypto) 📊</p>
                <p class="post-text">Locally deployable via browser (optionally with Docker) or as an Electron application</p>
                <p class="post-text">Currently deploying to heroku as well</p>
                <p class="post-text">Leveraging <a href="https://coinmarketcap.com/api/">CoinMarketCap</a> and <a href="https://www.alphavantage.co/">Alpha Advantage</a> APIs for market data</p>
                <p>👷‍♂️ <code>work in progress</code> 👷‍♂️</p>
              </div>
              <div class="centered-div">
                <hr/>
              </div>
              <div class="centered-div p-2">
                <div class="flex flex-row">
                  <h2 class="mr-2">recipls</h2>
                  <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/MaxRickettsUy/recipls-ui">
                    <img width="20" height="20" src={github}/>
                  </a>
                </div>
                <p class="post-text"><a href="https://golang.org/">Go</a> / <a href="https://vuejs.org/">Vue</a> weekly meal plan / recipe list generator 🍲 </p>
                <p class="post-text">Avenue for learning Golang and Vue</p>
                <p>👷‍♂️ <code>work in progress</code> 👷‍♂️</p>
              </div>
              <div class="centered-div">
                <hr/>
              </div>
              <div class="centered-div p-2">
                <div class="flex flex-row">
                  <a class="mr-2" href="https://prsnl.site">prsnl.site</a>
                  <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/MaxRickettsUy/prsnl.site">
                    <img width="20" height="20" src={github}/>
                  </a>
                </div>
                <p class="post-text">A curated collection of personal websites and blogs.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
      <Footer />
    </div>
  </body>
</Layout>